1
00:00:49,620 --> 00:00:53,820
=Camellias=

2
00:00:53,860 --> 00:00:56,780
=Episode 16=

3
00:01:01,960 --> 00:01:03,840
I was out fishing, like usual,

4
00:01:03,840 --> 00:01:05,560
when I saw several bodies.

5
00:01:05,560 --> 00:01:06,760
From their clothes, I can tell

6
00:01:06,760 --> 00:01:08,040
they were noble ladies from the palace.

7
00:01:08,040 --> 00:01:09,680
So I reported it to the authorities.

8
00:01:11,159 --> 00:01:11,640
How pitiful.

9
00:01:11,640 --> 00:01:12,959
These palace noble ladies,

10
00:01:12,959 --> 00:01:15,480
Lord Nine-Thousand took them
away early on.

11
00:01:15,480 --> 00:01:17,200
He's a eunuch.

12
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:21,280
Why would he take noble ladies?

13
00:01:21,560 --> 00:01:22,719
Naturally,

14
00:01:22,719 --> 00:01:23,560
to satisfy his

15
00:01:23,560 --> 00:01:24,719
twisted desires.

16
00:01:24,719 --> 00:01:25,680
I've heard

17
00:01:25,680 --> 00:01:27,359
he doesn't spare

18
00:01:27,359 --> 00:01:28,640
young, handsome men either.

19
00:01:29,879 --> 00:01:31,079
He goes for everyone?

20
00:01:31,079 --> 00:01:31,879
That's right.

21
00:01:36,760 --> 00:01:37,760
Now, noble ladies are found
drowned in the river,

22
00:01:37,760 --> 00:01:38,840
and rumors are spreading.

23
00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:40,439
Zhu Yunqi must be striking back.

24
00:01:43,200 --> 00:01:44,599
I'm not surprised at all.

25
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:47,200
Waiting around

26
00:01:48,079 --> 00:01:50,000
was never his style.

27
00:01:50,719 --> 00:01:52,040
You really know him well.

28
00:01:52,040 --> 00:01:52,840
My Lord.

29
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:53,799
My Lord.

30
00:01:54,840 --> 00:01:55,439
My Lord.

31
00:01:55,599 --> 00:01:57,040
His Majesty summons you to the palace.

32
00:01:57,040 --> 00:01:58,799
Summoning you now.

33
00:01:58,799 --> 00:01:59,840
It must be a trap.

34
00:02:01,760 --> 00:02:02,439
What's wrong?

35
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:05,319
You're already worried about me

36
00:02:05,319 --> 00:02:07,040
before I've even left?

37
00:02:07,599 --> 00:02:08,919
How did I never notice

38
00:02:08,919 --> 00:02:09,919
you could be so unserious?

39
00:02:09,919 --> 00:02:11,039
I'm worried...

40
00:02:11,879 --> 00:02:12,240
Enough.

41
00:02:12,240 --> 00:02:13,120
Don't worry about me.

42
00:02:13,759 --> 00:02:14,840
I have to go.

43
00:02:15,039 --> 00:02:15,560
If I don't,

44
00:02:15,560 --> 00:02:16,520
it's defying the imperial decree.

45
00:02:16,520 --> 00:02:17,199
And that would give him

46
00:02:17,199 --> 00:02:18,319
the perfect excuse to move against me.

47
00:02:20,159 --> 00:02:21,039
But you...

48
00:02:26,680 --> 00:02:27,360
Don't worry.

49
00:02:28,199 --> 00:02:29,120
I know what I'm doing.

50
00:02:51,719 --> 00:02:52,400
Greetings,

51
00:02:53,400 --> 00:02:54,439
Your Majesty.

52
00:02:54,879 --> 00:02:56,280
Rise, my dear minister.

53
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:57,280
Thank you, Your Majesty.

54
00:02:58,120 --> 00:02:58,879
My dear minister.

55
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:00,280
I've heard

56
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:02,560
that several female bodies were found
in the city river recently.

57
00:03:02,560 --> 00:03:03,439
Upon investigation,

58
00:03:03,439 --> 00:03:04,879
they were my noble ladies.

59
00:03:05,080 --> 00:03:06,280
I wonder

60
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:08,080
whether you are aware of this?

61
00:03:08,360 --> 00:03:09,360
I've heard some rumors.

62
00:03:09,719 --> 00:03:11,000
May I ask,

63
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:13,479
are you assigning this case to me?

64
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:15,080
You murderer!

65
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:16,039
Before His Majesty,

66
00:03:16,039 --> 00:03:18,280
you show no shame or remorse!

67
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:19,919
You killed my daughter!

68
00:03:20,639 --> 00:03:21,319
Minister.

69
00:03:24,159 --> 00:03:26,199
You need evidence to make
such accusations.

70
00:03:27,879 --> 00:03:29,479
I've never even met your daughter.

71
00:03:29,479 --> 00:03:30,879
How could I have harmed her?

72
00:03:30,879 --> 00:03:31,719
My daughter

73
00:03:31,960 --> 00:03:34,360
was one of the noble ladies
who drowned in the river.

74
00:03:34,560 --> 00:03:36,680
She trained at your manor before.

75
00:03:36,680 --> 00:03:37,479
Back then,

76
00:03:37,479 --> 00:03:39,080
you already had your eye on her.

77
00:03:39,080 --> 00:03:40,199
After she entered the palace,

78
00:03:40,199 --> 00:03:41,680
you used His Majesty's favor

79
00:03:41,680 --> 00:03:42,719
to take her back.

80
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:44,000
Your evil deeds

81
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:45,319
are known to all!

82
00:03:45,599 --> 00:03:47,439
Give me back my daughter's life!

83
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:49,360
Minister, calm down.

84
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:51,120
- Minister, calm down.
- Let go of me!

85
00:03:51,919 --> 00:03:52,680
Let go!

86
00:03:52,680 --> 00:03:54,439
What a touching display
of fatherly love.

87
00:03:56,280 --> 00:03:58,159
While she was at your manor,

88
00:03:59,639 --> 00:04:00,479
did she ever receive

89
00:04:00,479 --> 00:04:02,080
any love from you as a father?

90
00:04:02,439 --> 00:04:03,599
Don't change the subject.

91
00:04:03,599 --> 00:04:04,439
I loved my daughter

92
00:04:04,439 --> 00:04:05,560
with all my heart.

93
00:04:05,560 --> 00:04:06,560
She was my treasure.

94
00:04:07,960 --> 00:04:08,319
You,

95
00:04:08,599 --> 00:04:09,000
and you.

96
00:04:09,280 --> 00:04:10,280
All the women in your families

97
00:04:10,479 --> 00:04:11,680
were harmed by this man.

98
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:12,919
Say something, all of you.

99
00:04:12,919 --> 00:04:13,800
Speak up!

100
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:14,479
His Majesty

101
00:04:14,479 --> 00:04:16,399
will surely bring us justice!

102
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:19,319
We beg you, Your Majesty.
Bring us justice!

103
00:04:19,720 --> 00:04:22,959
Bring us justice!

104
00:04:29,639 --> 00:04:30,399
My dear minister.

105
00:04:30,759 --> 00:04:32,000
I've thought it over.

106
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:33,439
I still trust you.

107
00:04:39,759 --> 00:04:40,639
Thank you, Your Majesty.

108
00:04:41,959 --> 00:04:43,040
Then I

109
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:44,279
shall take my leave.

110
00:04:55,319 --> 00:04:56,879
But with the evidence here,

111
00:04:56,879 --> 00:04:58,040
I can't, for your sake,

112
00:04:58,040 --> 00:05:00,199
break the hearts of my other ministers.

113
00:05:00,879 --> 00:05:01,560
Holy Maiden.

114
00:05:02,480 --> 00:05:03,120
Holy Maiden.

115
00:05:04,240 --> 00:05:05,000
What's wrong?

116
00:05:05,480 --> 00:05:06,519
Has something happened to him?

117
00:05:06,519 --> 00:05:07,120
Holy Maiden.

118
00:05:07,319 --> 00:05:08,680
According to our scouts,

119
00:05:08,839 --> 00:05:09,839
His Majesty

120
00:05:09,839 --> 00:05:10,639
had this planned all along.

121
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:11,800
He's joined forces with

122
00:05:11,800 --> 00:05:13,319
the court officials

123
00:05:13,319 --> 00:05:14,079
to impeach My Lord,

124
00:05:14,079 --> 00:05:14,879
claiming that

125
00:05:14,879 --> 00:05:15,360
the noble ladies

126
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:16,000
and guards he saved

127
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:17,439
were all tortured to death by him.

128
00:05:17,439 --> 00:05:18,360
And those officials,

129
00:05:18,360 --> 00:05:19,360
who never treated their own daughters

130
00:05:19,360 --> 00:05:20,439
like human beings,

131
00:05:20,439 --> 00:05:21,160
are now all putting on

132
00:05:21,160 --> 00:05:22,319
a loving father act.

133
00:05:22,319 --> 00:05:23,839
They can't tell right from wrong.

134
00:05:24,120 --> 00:05:25,639
They twist the truth.

135
00:05:25,639 --> 00:05:27,560
My sister was right.

136
00:05:27,759 --> 00:05:29,199
This whole world is wrong.

137
00:05:29,199 --> 00:05:29,680
Holy Maiden.

138
00:05:30,360 --> 00:05:31,439
Before My Lord entered the palace,

139
00:05:31,680 --> 00:05:32,560
he instructed me

140
00:05:32,560 --> 00:05:33,480
to keep you safe.

141
00:05:33,759 --> 00:05:35,120
Please don't act impulsively.

142
00:05:37,680 --> 00:05:38,480
I know

143
00:05:39,680 --> 00:05:41,319
acting impulsively won't help.

144
00:05:41,680 --> 00:05:43,000
Zhu Yunqi

145
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:44,800
won't stop here either.

146
00:05:49,439 --> 00:05:50,240
Feng Liu.

147
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:52,160
There's still one way.

148
00:06:03,399 --> 00:06:04,160
Feng Ye.

149
00:06:05,319 --> 00:06:06,399
You should know

150
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:07,920
that I would never move against you

151
00:06:07,920 --> 00:06:09,720
unless I had no other choice.

152
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:11,079
Say no more.

153
00:06:11,680 --> 00:06:12,839
We've both made

154
00:06:12,839 --> 00:06:13,920
our own choices.

155
00:06:13,920 --> 00:06:15,240
If you're willing to turn back,

156
00:06:15,240 --> 00:06:16,160
I can still, just as

157
00:06:16,160 --> 00:06:17,439
I said back in the forsaken palace,

158
00:06:17,639 --> 00:06:18,639
share this realm

159
00:06:18,959 --> 00:06:20,680
with you!

160
00:06:20,680 --> 00:06:21,879
Then do you still remember

161
00:06:21,879 --> 00:06:22,959
the vows we made

162
00:06:22,959 --> 00:06:24,600
back in the forsaken palace?

163
00:06:43,040 --> 00:06:44,120
(Don't be afraid.)

164
00:06:44,519 --> 00:06:45,600
(I'll help you.)

165
00:06:54,399 --> 00:06:55,680
It seems

166
00:06:55,920 --> 00:06:58,240
you're still set on your path.

167
00:06:58,240 --> 00:07:00,480
I'm only staying true to myself.

168
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:03,079
(Donghua Gate)
By the grace of Heaven,

169
00:07:03,079 --> 00:07:04,120
(Donghua Gate)
the Emperor

170
00:07:04,120 --> 00:07:05,519
decrees:

171
00:07:05,519 --> 00:07:07,399
Lord Nine-Thousand Feng Ye,

172
00:07:07,399 --> 00:07:09,160
whose power overshadows the court,

173
00:07:09,160 --> 00:07:11,240
has defied the laws of the state

174
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:12,879
and cruelly slain noble ladies.

175
00:07:12,879 --> 00:07:14,680
The evidence is conclusive.

176
00:07:14,680 --> 00:07:16,160
To uphold justice,

177
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:17,920
he is hereby sentenced to beheading

178
00:07:17,920 --> 00:07:19,920
and public execution.

179
00:07:20,079 --> 00:07:22,319
This is the decree.

180
00:07:23,519 --> 00:07:24,759
A eunuch like him

181
00:07:24,759 --> 00:07:25,959
harming women?

182
00:07:25,959 --> 00:07:27,040
He deserves to die.

183
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:28,000
I heard

184
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:30,399
he took all those women

185
00:07:30,399 --> 00:07:31,680
to satisfy his sick, depraved desires.

186
00:07:31,680 --> 00:07:32,560
Yes, he should die.

187
00:07:32,560 --> 00:07:34,360
Lord Nine-Thousand has been
my trusted confidant.

188
00:07:34,680 --> 00:07:35,959
But I never imagined

189
00:07:35,959 --> 00:07:37,959
he could be so cruel.

190
00:07:38,319 --> 00:07:39,639
Spreading rumors everywhere,

191
00:07:39,639 --> 00:07:41,560
trying to pin all these crimes

192
00:07:41,879 --> 00:07:44,040
on me.

193
00:07:47,439 --> 00:07:49,480
It truly breaks my heart.

194
00:07:51,920 --> 00:07:54,199
Your Majesty, please take care
of your health.

195
00:07:57,959 --> 00:07:58,839
Today,

196
00:07:59,040 --> 00:08:00,759
I place his life

197
00:08:00,759 --> 00:08:02,279
in your hands.

198
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:04,040
Tell me.

199
00:08:04,439 --> 00:08:05,720
Does he deserve to die?

200
00:08:09,240 --> 00:08:10,360
Your Majesty is merciful.

201
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:12,439
But a useless eunuch like him
has no place in this world.

202
00:08:12,839 --> 00:08:13,600
Kill!

203
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:14,879
Kill him!

204
00:08:14,879 --> 00:08:16,000
Kill him!

205
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:16,920
Kill!

206
00:08:17,120 --> 00:08:17,920
Kill!

207
00:08:18,319 --> 00:08:18,720
Kill!

208
00:08:18,720 --> 00:08:19,360
I'm sorry.

209
00:08:19,560 --> 00:08:20,120
Kill!

210
00:08:20,120 --> 00:08:20,800
Yukui.

211
00:08:20,800 --> 00:08:27,240
Kill!

212
00:08:56,820 --> 00:08:58,279
(Squire Lin)

213
00:08:58,279 --> 00:08:59,480
(Squire Lin)
Shuang.

214
00:09:04,399 --> 00:09:05,679
(Mercy, Your Majesty!)

215
00:09:05,679 --> 00:09:07,720
(I'm truly carrying your child!)

216
00:09:07,720 --> 00:09:08,679
(Guards.)

217
00:09:08,679 --> 00:09:09,840
(Cut open her belly!)

218
00:09:24,080 --> 00:09:25,200
(What happened to My Lord?)

219
00:09:25,600 --> 00:09:27,480
(To condemn My Lord,)

220
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:30,080
(His Majesty claims he harmed
you noble ladies.)

221
00:09:31,240 --> 00:09:32,279
(Now,)

222
00:09:32,279 --> 00:09:33,879
(My Lord is in grave danger.)

223
00:09:35,240 --> 00:09:37,399
(Only you can help him.)

224
00:09:37,399 --> 00:09:39,080
(I'll go back with you now.)

225
00:09:39,080 --> 00:09:40,679
(My Lord saved me)

226
00:09:40,679 --> 00:09:41,720
(from a living hell.)

227
00:09:42,240 --> 00:09:43,200
(At worst,)

228
00:09:43,519 --> 00:09:45,360
(I'll give my life back to him.)

229
00:10:15,559 --> 00:10:16,000
Look.

230
00:10:16,399 --> 00:10:17,519
Isn't she dead?

231
00:10:32,159 --> 00:10:34,360
My Lord never mistreated me.

232
00:10:34,720 --> 00:10:35,960
On the contrary,

233
00:10:35,960 --> 00:10:38,039
he saved me from a heartless family

234
00:10:38,039 --> 00:10:40,679
and a brutal inner palace.

235
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:43,240
Yet he's the one bearing all the blame,

236
00:10:44,039 --> 00:10:46,720
and that gave you the opening
to impeach him.

237
00:10:53,960 --> 00:10:54,759
Shuang.

238
00:10:55,519 --> 00:10:56,679
You're alive?

239
00:10:57,279 --> 00:10:58,600
Thank goodness.

240
00:11:01,480 --> 00:11:02,279
Shuang.

241
00:11:02,519 --> 00:11:03,279
Don't be afraid.

242
00:11:03,840 --> 00:11:05,480
Speak the truth boldly.

243
00:11:05,480 --> 00:11:07,159
I will seek justice for you.

244
00:11:07,559 --> 00:11:09,440
What I just said is the truth.

245
00:11:09,440 --> 00:11:11,039
What nonsense are you saying?

246
00:11:11,879 --> 00:11:13,799
Is Feng Ye coercing you

247
00:11:13,799 --> 00:11:14,919
into saying all this?

248
00:11:14,919 --> 00:11:17,159
My Lord never coerced me.

249
00:11:18,000 --> 00:11:20,440
The one who truly coerced me is you.

250
00:11:20,720 --> 00:11:21,200
I...

251
00:11:22,080 --> 00:11:23,600
Since the day I was born,

252
00:11:24,080 --> 00:11:25,960
have you ever truly cared for me?

253
00:11:26,840 --> 00:11:27,799
To you,

254
00:11:27,799 --> 00:11:29,200
I was nothing more

255
00:11:29,200 --> 00:11:31,720
than a tool to gain wealth and power.

256
00:11:32,360 --> 00:11:34,000
If I couldn't serve your purposes,

257
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:36,360
you would cast me aside
without hesitation,

258
00:11:36,360 --> 00:11:37,679
even kill me.

259
00:11:39,960 --> 00:11:41,279
Mr. Fu and I

260
00:11:41,759 --> 00:11:43,320
were already engaged,

261
00:11:43,320 --> 00:11:44,639
and we loved each other.

262
00:11:45,159 --> 00:11:46,000
But you,

263
00:11:46,200 --> 00:11:48,039
for your own selfish gain,

264
00:11:48,039 --> 00:11:49,960
tore us apart

265
00:11:49,960 --> 00:11:51,240
and sent me to the palace.

266
00:11:51,399 --> 00:11:52,399
And you,

267
00:11:55,480 --> 00:11:57,480
the ruler of a nation,

268
00:11:57,840 --> 00:11:59,840
only care about pleasure and amusement.

269
00:11:59,840 --> 00:12:00,679
To you,

270
00:12:00,679 --> 00:12:01,519
all of us women

271
00:12:01,519 --> 00:12:03,759
are nothing but playthings
to vent your anger.

272
00:12:04,480 --> 00:12:06,200
From the moment I entered the palace,

273
00:12:06,200 --> 00:12:08,919
you never once treated me as a human.

274
00:12:09,759 --> 00:12:11,120
By the time Mr. Fu entered the palace,

275
00:12:11,120 --> 00:12:12,639
he had already been made a eunuch.

276
00:12:13,679 --> 00:12:14,919
Yet you still, because

277
00:12:14,919 --> 00:12:16,639
of a single word from Consort Rong,

278
00:12:16,639 --> 00:12:18,600
claimed I had an affair with him

279
00:12:19,320 --> 00:12:21,200
and had his tongue cut out.

280
00:12:25,159 --> 00:12:27,720
And because of a bet between you two,

281
00:12:28,440 --> 00:12:30,279
you had my belly cut open

282
00:12:30,279 --> 00:12:32,000
in public to check the baby's sex.

283
00:12:42,240 --> 00:12:42,799
You...

284
00:12:44,320 --> 00:12:45,840
You unfilial daughter!

285
00:12:45,840 --> 00:12:47,120
Baring yourself in public,

286
00:12:47,120 --> 00:12:48,960
have you no shame?

287
00:12:49,200 --> 00:12:50,360
Shame?

288
00:12:50,360 --> 00:12:52,360
Why should I feel shame?

289
00:12:52,360 --> 00:12:54,759
You dare speak to me of shame?

290
00:12:55,200 --> 00:12:56,679
The ones who should be ashamed

291
00:12:56,679 --> 00:12:58,120
are those who left

292
00:12:58,120 --> 00:12:59,919
their marks on my body.

293
00:12:59,919 --> 00:13:01,440
You, the father who gave me life

294
00:13:01,440 --> 00:13:03,399
but never raised me,
are a selfish villain!

295
00:13:03,399 --> 00:13:04,080
You...

296
00:13:04,600 --> 00:13:06,519
How dare you speak

297
00:13:06,519 --> 00:13:08,320
such treasonous words!

298
00:13:10,320 --> 00:13:11,840
Everyone, don't listen to her.

299
00:13:12,399 --> 00:13:14,639
Feng Ye is skilled
at manipulating minds.

300
00:13:14,639 --> 00:13:16,519
He must have bewitched my daughter!

301
00:13:16,840 --> 00:13:18,200
He might bewitch one person,

302
00:13:18,200 --> 00:13:20,039
but can he bewitch all of us?

303
00:13:20,919 --> 00:13:22,399
I am Zhang Menghu.

304
00:13:22,519 --> 00:13:23,519
Does Your Majesty remember

305
00:13:23,519 --> 00:13:25,039
the lantern festival three years ago?

306
00:13:25,519 --> 00:13:26,679
The poisoned wine you bestowed,

307
00:13:26,679 --> 00:13:28,360
My Lord swapped it for an antidote.

308
00:13:28,720 --> 00:13:29,879
That's why I wasn't

309
00:13:29,879 --> 00:13:32,039
fed to the wild dogs in the mass grave.

310
00:13:32,600 --> 00:13:33,399
I am

311
00:13:33,399 --> 00:13:34,279
Li Wanping.

312
00:13:34,919 --> 00:13:36,120
Last year on the Lantern Festival,

313
00:13:36,320 --> 00:13:38,440
you said I offended you by wearing red.

314
00:13:38,440 --> 00:13:40,360
You wanted me strangled
beneath the palace walls.

315
00:13:41,080 --> 00:13:43,480
My Lord's men from the Nanfeng Pavilion
broke in that night

316
00:13:43,600 --> 00:13:45,440
and sent me out of the capital
in their own carriage.

317
00:13:45,840 --> 00:13:46,600
I am

318
00:13:46,600 --> 00:13:47,200
Liu Hongdou.

319
00:13:47,639 --> 00:13:49,600
Consort Rong said I knocked over
an imperial incense burner.

320
00:13:49,600 --> 00:13:51,399
And she wanted me flayed alive.

321
00:13:51,840 --> 00:13:53,440
My Lord's shadow guards,

322
00:13:53,440 --> 00:13:54,399
under cover of night,

323
00:13:54,399 --> 00:13:55,840
rescued me from the woodshed.

324
00:13:56,240 --> 00:13:57,320
My worthless life,

325
00:13:57,600 --> 00:13:59,039
I owe it all to My Lord.

326
00:13:59,840 --> 00:14:01,039
These officials,

327
00:14:01,200 --> 00:14:02,120
they shoved us

328
00:14:02,120 --> 00:14:03,519
straight into the fire,

329
00:14:03,519 --> 00:14:05,279
turning us into playthings for others.

330
00:14:05,799 --> 00:14:07,919
If My Lord hadn't saved us,

331
00:14:07,919 --> 00:14:08,600
we would have ended up

332
00:14:08,600 --> 00:14:10,399
like those noble ladies
found dead in the river,

333
00:14:10,399 --> 00:14:12,559
tortured by Zhu Yunqi.

334
00:14:12,840 --> 00:14:14,080
My Lord is innocent!

335
00:14:14,080 --> 00:14:15,440
Free My Lord!

336
00:14:15,440 --> 00:14:16,159
Guards!

337
00:14:16,159 --> 00:14:17,279
Seize them all!

338
00:14:17,279 --> 00:14:17,919
Hurry!

339
00:14:17,919 --> 00:14:19,200
Hurry!

340
00:14:36,660 --> 00:14:38,060
♪The moon sinks in the west♪

341
00:14:38,540 --> 00:14:39,980
♪The cold lamp burns low♪

342
00:14:40,180 --> 00:14:43,300
♪No one knocks upon
the mountain gate♪

343
00:14:43,620 --> 00:14:47,420
♪Snow-white winds and moonlight
touch me first♪

344
00:14:50,380 --> 00:14:52,100
♪Pear blossoms fill the courtyard♪

345
00:14:52,100 --> 00:14:53,620
♪Yet love and hate entwine♪

346
00:14:53,980 --> 00:14:57,380
♪Bound by precepts,
yet craving worldly desires♪

347
00:14:57,380 --> 00:15:01,380
♪Gathering red beans
for half a lifetime♪

348
00:15:02,540 --> 00:15:05,700
♪The Buddha speaks of countless paths♪

349
00:15:05,700 --> 00:15:09,260
♪How can one glance spanning ages
save a wandering soul♪

350
00:15:09,260 --> 00:15:11,580
♪Trapped within
the space between your brows♪

351
00:15:11,580 --> 00:15:15,780
♪Falling deeper and deeper♪

352
00:15:16,220 --> 00:15:17,860
♪The green lamp sheds no light♪

353
00:15:17,860 --> 00:15:19,380
♪Upon one who entered the path♪

354
00:15:19,380 --> 00:15:22,580
♪The six senses cannot cleanse
the dust of the past♪

355
00:15:22,980 --> 00:15:24,900
♪In dreams, it's you♪

356
00:15:24,900 --> 00:15:26,300
♪Beyond dreams, no one♪

357
00:15:26,300 --> 00:15:29,620
♪Clinging to one obsession,
adrift in a sea of suffering♪

358
00:15:29,620 --> 00:15:33,020
♪I can't forget the stars in your eyes♪

359
00:15:33,020 --> 00:15:36,580
♪Our fate had already taken root♪

360
00:15:36,580 --> 00:15:39,820
♪In this mortal world, there is only us♪

361
00:15:39,820 --> 00:15:43,260
♪Hopelessly bound by love♪
